        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 14. Megophrys serchhipii referred specimens showing variation in life: (a–b). adult male (SDBDU 2007.1517: SVL 41.3 mm) from Tamenglong district, Manipur state, India: (a). dorsolateral view; (b). ventral view; (c–d). adult male (SDBDU 2009.580: SVL 45.1 mm) from Gomati district, Tripura state, India: (c). dorsolateral view; (d). ventral view; (e). adult male (SDBDU 2011.464: SVL 41.0 mm) from West Garo Hills district, Meghalaya state, India, lateral view; (f). adult female (JU 0042: SVL 53.6 mm) from Chittagong division, Bangladesh, lateral view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4608930/files/figure.png" .

